rows.label: tlk70000074_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Your Majesty! How was the
Iiran capital?

rows.label: tlk70000074_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Did you achieve unrivaled prosperity
for Superbia?

rows.label: tlk70000074_03_msg0003
rows.name:
How wonderful... Shall I see to this
as special envoy? I have had an interest
in Iiran culture for some time now...

rows.label: tlk70000074_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I must remain here as the Gula
special envoy? Why, Your Majesty?!
I am sure you have your reasons, but...

rows.label: tlk70000074_03_msg0005
rows.name:
But...my interests in Iiran food and
architecture, and... But... But my direct
imperial orders...

rows.label: tlk70000074_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Uh? You were "merely jesting"...?
I... Your Highness...
You just knocked 10 years off me...
